License

The R code and documentation in this repository are shared for educational purposes as part of the course Digital Archives and Methods, Spring 2026.
The code may be reused and adapted for non-commercial educational and research purposes, provided that the authors are credited.
The source texts used in this project are official and publicly available apology texts collected from the Prime Minister’s Office and Danske Taler. These texts belong to their original publishers/authors and are included here only for documentation and reproducibility of the course project.

